data.description: Single Family Home for sale by owner in Johnson City, NY 13790. Newly Remodeled 3 bedroom, 1 bath home with garage. This home has many new features. In 2011 the following was done: New High Efficiency Furnace and Ductwork New Water Tank (Natural Gas - 50 gal.) New Dryer (Natural Gas) New Washer (Electric) New Electric Panel Box New Electric Wiring - Basement and First Floor Newly Updated Kitchen Cabinets, Countertops and Sink New Stainless Steel Refrigerator New Stainless Steel Stove (Electric) Newly Updated Living Room (surround sound wiring in walls) Newly Updated Dining Room New Front Door New Side Doors Garage (Insulation, Drywall and Electric) 1st Floor was completely redone. New floors, carpets, insulation and walls. In 2012 the following was done: Additional room added in the basement New Back Deck Flooring (needs stained) Garage has a garage door opener and rubber flooring that stays. Nice home in a nice location. Park with picnic area and playground is just around
